<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="concentration-n">concentration <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌkɒnsen'treɪʃn/    美 /ˌkɒnsen'treɪʃən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 集中；专心：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Concentration on</strong> your studies will result in good grades.
专心学习就能取得优异的成绩。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Driving requires total concentration.
开车时需要全神贯注。</p></div></div>